OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be mainly dry with late
OL,7,Fbrightness in places, chance of the
OL,8,Fodd shower in the south and east. The
OL,9,Frest of the night will will be dry
OL,10,Fwith clear spells, especially in the
OL,11,Feast. .
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FGood sunny spells between
OL,14,Fpatchy amounts of cloud. Most places
OL,15,Fwill remain dry, but the odd light
OL,16,Fpassing shower possible in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
